==== TromaNightAdventure ====
=== PaulMann ===
----
**"Do you want to come to [[TromaNight Troma Night]]?"**

Paul looks happy.

//"[[TromaNight Troma Night]] is tonight? I'd forgotten! Why didn't you remind me, rather than going through that farce!"//

{{InvPickup item="PaulMann"}}

//"I've got this film we ought to watch... it's the one I told you about - the really bad one with the guy that does the thing with that person: you know, the one from the TV series about that place..."//

{{InvPickup item="Really Bad Film"}} {{Test if="!hasItem(Manhole Opener)" then="\n\nPaul returns your Manhole Opener.\n\n~{InvPickup item=~Manhole Opener~}~"}}
----
**What next?**
~- [[TromaNight164 "Great, let's go!"]]

==== TromaNightAdventure ====
=== ArtsCentreTheatre @ AberystwythArtsCentre ===
----
//"Do you have a ticket?"// asks the usherette.

**"Umm... no..."**

MisterJTA steps in.

//"I,"// he says, with a huge emphasis, //"am an **actor**!"//

//"Oh,"// says the usherette, //"Go right in, then."//

[[MisterJTA JTA]] disappears into the theatre. After a little while, he returns.

{{Test if="!hasItem(Length Of Rope)" then="You hear a crash like a set falling down on stage. MisterJTA runs out, carrying a length of rope.\n\n~{InvPickup item=~Length Of Rope~}~" else="MisterJTA reports that there's nothing of interest in the theatre."}}
----
**What next?**
~- [[TromaNight100 Leave the ArtsCentreTheatre]]

