==== TromaNightAdventure ====
=== DanHuntley ===
----
**"What extra challenges might I like to complete?"**

//"You don't think that saving TromaNight is enough? All right then:"//

//"First and foremost, there are extra points available for getting **more** than the required quota of TromaNight stars. Secondly, you can also earn extra points by bringing more pizza or more films than are required."//

//"Thirdly: try to solve the challenges that confront you in the way that best shows off your abilities. If you have the choice between doing something yourself, and getting another star to do it, the former will earn you more points."//

//"More specific challenges (which earn points) include:"//

=== TromaNightAdventure Extra Challenges ===
~- Having //both// items that can be used to get AndyKeohane to come to TromaNight.

//"Will that be all?"//
----
**What next?**
~- [[TromaNightD01 "Can I ask you something else?"]]
~- [[TromaNight002 "That's all, thanks."]]

Who owns the best page on RockMonkey. Leave their name and page title below;

The best page on rockmonkey is [[Lesbians]]. Why do we have to leave the owners' name? Unless [[AndyKeohane Andy]] steals it it's not going to change!
 - Just makes it look neat and tidy and... well... just because.

==== TromaNightAdventure ====
=== Railway Station ===
----
{{image class="center" alt="Aberystwyth Pier" url="/TromaNightAdventure/abersign01.jpg"}}

You are at [[AberystwythTown Aberystwyth]] railway station. {{InvHasNone item="MisterJTA" text="A train has just pulled in, and people are milling about, trying to find one another and gather their bags, children, and other inconveniences. Amongst the throng, you think you make out a familiar face - could it be MisterJTA?"}} {{InvHasOne item="MisterJTA" text="The hubbub has cleared and the platform is clear. JTA seems relieved that he doesn't have to fight his way through the crowd any more."}}
----
**What next?** {{Test if="!hasItem(MisterJTA)" then="\n~- [[TromaNight007a Try to find MisterJTA]]"}}
~- [[TromaNight003 Leave the station]]

==== TromaNightAdventure ====
=== Shell Filling Station ===
----
You find yourself in the forecourt of the Shell filling station. People are filling up their cars with fuel. On the other side of a glass hatch, an attendant in his early twenties is becoming more and more frustrated with having to push stupidly-shaped items through the slot that seperates him from his customers. {{InvHasOne item="PaulMann" text="Paul hums a chorus of '24 hour garage people'."}}

There's a manhole-style hatch near the fire extinguishers. {{Test if="getToken(policeatshell) = 2 and getToken(policepranked) = 0" then="\n\nThere's a heavy police presence around the filling station. It looks like the onwer got wise to your scam."}}
----
**What next?** {{Test if="getToken(policeatshell) = 2 and getToken(policepranked) = 0" then="\n~- [[TromaNight249 Talk to the Man-Behind-The-Hatch]]" else="\n~- [[TromaNight023 Talk to the Man-Behind-The-Hatch]]"}}
~- {{InvHasNone item="Manhole Opener" link="TromaNight024" text="Open the manhole"}} {{InvHasOne item="Manhole Opener" link="TromaNight025" text="Open the manhole"}}
~- [[TromaNight003 Return to Alexandra Terrace]]

==== TromaNightAdventure ====
=== North Beach ===
----
You are on North Beach, opposite The Bay hotel. The beach continues both to the South (where it takes a Southwesterly turn) and to the North. {{InvHasNone item="AndyKeohane" text="To the North, there is a figure moving around on the beach."}}
----
**What next?**
~- [[TromaNight040 Return to the promenade]] {{Test if="hasItem(Picture Of A Rock)" then="\n~- [[TromaNight081 Look for a rock for Andy]]"}} {{Test if="hasItem(Picture Of A Rock) and !hasItem(Fake Blue Rock) and !hasItem(AndyKeohane) and hasItem(Blue Paint)" then="\n~- [[TromaNight236 Paint a rock blue]]"}}
~- [[TromaNight051 Walk North, along the beach]]
~- [[TromaNight042 Walk South, along the beach]] {{Test if="hasItem(AndyKeohane)" text="\n~- [[TromaNight254 Ask Andy, 'What's That Rock?']]"}}

==== TromaNightAdventure ====
=== North Beach ===
----
{{Test if="hasItem(AndyKeohane)" then="~{image class=~center~ alt=~Beach Under Constitution Hill~ url=~/TromaNightAdventure/const_beach.jpg~}~" else="~{image class=~center~ alt=~Beach Under Constitution Hill~ url=~/TromaNightAdventure/const_beach_andy.jpg~}~"}}

You are at the far Northernmost end of North Beach - travelling further North is impossible while the tide is as high as it is. Constitution Hill looms over you, and you can see - on the promenade - the ticket office for the funicular railway. {{InvHasNone item="AndyKeohane" text="AndyKeohane is here, moving around in the darkness and occasionally stopping to pick up and examine a pebble, before putting it down again and shaking his head."}}
----
**What next?**
~- [[TromaNight061 Return to the promenade]] {{Test if="!hasItem(AndyKeohane)" then="\n~- [[TromaNight065 Talk to AndyKeohane]]"}} {{Test if="hasItem(Picture Of A Rock)" then="\n~- [[TromaNight082 Look for a rock for Andy]]"}} {{Test if="hasItem(Picture Of A Rock) and !hasItem(Fake Blue Rock) and !hasItem(AndyKeohane) and hasItem(Blue Paint)" then="\n~- [[TromaNight235 Paint a rock blue]]"}}
~- [[TromaNight050 Walk South along the beach]] {{Test if="hasItem(AndyKeohane)" then="\n~- [[TromaNight255 Ask Andy, 'What's That Rock?']]"}}

==== TromaNightAdventure ====
=== GeographyTower Roof ===
----
{{image class="center" alt=Geography Building" url="/TromaNightAdventure/Geography.jpg"}}

You are on the roof of the GeographyTower. The view is spectacular: the lights of the town are just being turned on, and you can make out people moving around on campus. {{InvHasNone item="PaulMann" text="Looks like there's somebody moving around on the roof of the students union."}}
----
**What next?** {{Test if="hasItem(Length Of Rope)" then="\n~- [[TromaNight126 Abseil down the tower using your rope]]"}}
~- [[TromaNight121 Back into the tower]]

==== TromaNightAdventure ====
=== ComputerScience Student ===
----
//"That's a SoundMaster Pro 7000! A wonderful piece of audio hardware. Tell you what: if you're ever short of dough, I'll buy as many of them as you like from you!"//
----
**What next?** {{Test if="!hasItem(Heaps Of Cash)" then="\n~- [[TromaNight132 Sell the soundcard to the geek]]"}}
~- {{InvHasNone item="Heaps Of Cash" link="TromaNight130" text="I think I'll keep it, for now: it might have another use"}} {{InvHasOne item="Heaps Of Cash" link="TromaNight130" text="I've already got plenty of money"}}

==== TromaNightAdventure ====
=== Roof Of The [[StudentsUnion]] Building ===
----
You are on the roof of the StudentsUnion building, on PenglaisCampus. The view would be great, if it weren't for L'Escala out on the concourse - a large concrete stairwell to nowhere at all. You can clearly see the HughOwen Library and AberystwythArtsCentre accross the concourse, as well as some of PenglaisCampus's other buildings, such as the PhysicsBuilding and GeographyTower.

There's a trapdoor here with a self-locking catch on the top. You could go down through it, but you wouldn't be able to return by that route. And most unexpectedly, there is a manhole here: it has a square cover. {{Test if="!hasItem(PaulMann)" then="\n\nPaulMann is milling around on the roof, manipulating several strange pieces of unidentifiable hand-held equipment." else="[[PaulMann Paul]] hums the '[[http://www.toonhound.com/trapdoor.htm Trapdoor]]' theme."}}
----
**What next?**
~- [[TromaNight101 Go down the trapdoor]] {{Test if="!hasItem(PaulMann)" then="\n~- [[TromaNight165 Talk to Paul]]"}}
~- {{InvHasNone item="Manhole Opener" link="TromaNight201" text="Open the manhole"}} {{InvHasOne item="Manhole Opener" link="TromaNight196" text="Open the manhole"}}

