=== PaulMann ===
----
You give Paul your Manhole Opener.

{{InvDrop item="Manhole Opener"}}

{{Test if="!hasItem(Pile Of Sand)" then="Paul gives you a Pile Of Sand\n\n~{InvPickup item=~Pile Of Sand~}~" else="Paul makes a gesture like swimming."}} {{Test if="hasItem(Pile Of Sand) and hasItem(Jam Jar)" then="\n\nPaul indicates that you should put the sand into the jam jar."}}
