{{InvDrop item="Expensive Soundcard"}}

{{Test if="!hasItem(Jam Jar)" then="Paul gives you a Jam Jar\n\n~{InvPickup item=~Jam Jar~}~" else="Paul pretends to be a meercat."}} {{Test if="hasItem(Pile Of Sand) and hasItem(Jam Jar)" then="\n\nPaul indicates that you should put the sand into the jam jar."}}
