{{Test if="!hasItem(Pile Of Sand)" then="Paul gives you a Pile Of Sand\n\n~{InvPickup item=~Pile Of Sand~}~" else="Paul pokes your Pile Of Sand."}} {{Test if="hasItem(Pile Of Sand) and hasItem(Jam Jar)" then="\n\nPaul indicates that you should put the sand into the jam jar."}}
