==== TromaNightAdventure ====
=== GreatHall @ AberystwythArtsCentre ===
----
{{image class="center" alt="Great Hall" url="/TromaNightAdventure/Artscentre01.jpg"}}

You step into the warmth of the GreatHall. The seats are all empty, and some students are rehearsing a play on the main stage. One woman, in particular, seems to be involved in a particularly long monologue.

{{Test if="hasItem(Arty Film)" then="An empty black handbag sits beside the stage, where you left it. The woman on the stage eyes you curiously." else="A small black handbag sits beside the stage. You can see the tip of a DVD case protuding from the top of it. Your TromaSense starts tingling..."}}
----
**What next?** {{Test if="!hasItem(Arty Film)" then="\n~- [[TromaNight257 Steal the handbag]]"}} {{Test if="!hasItem(Arty Film)" then="\n~- [[TromaNight258 Steal the DVD from the handbag]]"}} {{Test if="!hasItem(Arty Film) and hasItem(Black Handbag)" then="\n~- [[TromaNight259 Switch the handbag with the one you're carrying]]"}}
~- [[TromaNight100 Leave the GreatHall]]

==== TromaNightAdventure ====
=== GreatHall @ AberystwythArtsCentre ===
----
{{image class="center" alt="Great Hall" url="/TromaNightAdventure/Artscentre01.jpg"}}

The woman on stage seems suspicious as you approach her handbag. You wait a moment until she looks away, and then... //yoink//... switch her handbag for the handbag you already had.

Outside the Great Hall, you empty it and claim your prize:

{{InvDrop item="Black Handbag"}}

{{InvPickup item="Arty Film"}}

{{InvPickup item="Notepad And Pen"}}
----
**What next?**
~- [[TromaNight100 That's one more film for Troma Night!]]

==== TromaNightAdventure ====
=== You Have Won! ===
----
**CONGRATULATIONS!** You have won TromaNightAdventure! {{SetToken token="finalscore" value="0"}} {{SetToken token="pantycelyn" value="0"}}
----
=== Score Breakdown ===
== People At TromaNight ==
~- {{Test if="hasItem(BrynSalisbury)" then="You rescued **BrynSalisbury** from a bucket! **(10pts)** ~{SetToken token=~finalscore~ value=~+10~}~" else="You didn't get **BrynSalisbury** to TromaNight. **(0pts)**"}}
~- {{Test if="hasItem(PaulMann)" then="You negotiated **PaulMann**'s appearance at TromaNight! **(10pts)** ~{SetToken token=~finalscore~ value=~+10~}~" else="You couldn't persuade **PaulMann** to come. **(0pts)**"}}
~- {{Test if="hasItem(RuthVarley)" then="You rescued **RuthVarley** from [[Pantycelyn]]! **(10pts)** ~{SetToken token=~finalscore~ value=~+10~}~" else="You didn't manage to rescue **RuthVarley**. **(0pts)**"}}
~- {{Test if="hasItem(MisterJTA)" then="You brought **MisterJTA** along! **(10pts)** ~{SetToken token=~finalscore~ value=~+10~}~" else="You didn't manage to get to **MisterJTA**. **(0pts)**"}}
~- {{Test if="hasItem(JonAtkinson)" then="With the promise of TastyLager, **JonAtkinson** came over! **(10pts)** ~{SetToken token=~finalscore~ value=~+10~}~" else="**JonAtkinson** decided he had better things to do. **(0pts)**"}}
~- {{Test if="hasItem(AndyKeohane)" then="He should be doing his coursework, but you got **AndyKeohane** to come to TromaNight anyway! **(10pts)** ~{SetToken token=~finalscore~ value=~+10~}~" else="**AndyKeohane** wouldn't come to TromaNight. **(0pts)**"}}

== TromaNight Films ==
~- {{Test if="hasItem(Really Bad Film)" then="[[PaulMann Paul]] provided the **Really Bad Film**! **(5pts)** ~{SetToken token=~finalscore~ value=~+5~}~" else="You didn't get the **Really Bad Film**. **(0pts)**"}}
~- {{Test if="hasItem(Really Good Film)" then="NotGayGareth lent you the **Really Good Film**! **(5pts)** ~{SetToken token=~finalscore~ value=~+5~}~" else="You failed to get the **Really Good Film**. **(0pts)**"}}
~- {{Test if="hasItem(Moderately Good Film)" then="You got the **Moderately Good Film** from PierVideo! **(5pts)** ~{SetToken token=~finalscore~ value=~+5~}~" else="There's no **Moderately Good Film** to watch, though. **(0pts)**"}}
~- {{Test if="hasItem(Arty Film)" then="You found the **Arty Film**! **(10pts)** ~{SetToken token=~finalscore~ value=~+10~}~" else="You didn't find the **Arty Film**. **(0pts)**"}}
~- {{Test if="hasItem(Pornographic Film)" then="And you also grabbed the **Pornographic Film**! **(10pts)** ~{SetToken token=~finalscore~ value=~+10~}~" else="You couldn't get the **Pornographic Film**. **(0pts)**"}}

== TromaNight Refreshments ==
~- {{Test if="hasItem(RealAle)" then="You acquired **RealAle**! **(10pts)** ~{SetToken token=~finalscore~ value=~+10~}~" else="You didn't get **RealAle**!!! **(-100pts)** ~{SetToken token=~finalscore~ value=~-100~}~"}}
~- {{Test if="hasItem(Pizza With Meat)" then="DanHuntley munches down on the **Pizza With Meat**! **(5pts)** ~{SetToken token=~finalscore~ value=~+5~}~" else="You didn't get any **Pizza With Meat**. **(0pts)**"}}
~- {{Test if="hasItem(Pizza With Vegetables)" then="You bought **Pizza With Vegetables** for the [[Vegetarian vegetarians]]. **(10pts)** ~{SetToken token=~finalscore~ value=~+5~}~" else="You didn't get any **Pizza With Vegetables**. **(0pts)**"}}
~- {{Test if="hasItem(Pizza With Everything)" then="The **Pizza With Everything** goes down a storm! **(10pts)** ~{SetToken token=~finalscore~ value=~+10~}~" else="But there's no **Pizza With Everything** for anybody. **(0pts)**"}}

== Pantycelyn Rescue == {{Test if="hasItem(Welsh Flag Towel)" then="\n~- You stole the **Welsh Flag Towel** from [[Pantycelyn]]! **(10pts)** ~{SetToken token=~finalscore~ value=~+10~}~ ~{SetToken token=~pantycelyn~ value=~1~}~"}} {{Test if="hasItem(A Sore Head)" then="\n~- You injured your head while escaping from [[Pantycelyn]]! **(-5pts)** ~{SetToken token=~finalscore~ value=~-5~}~ ~{SetToken token=~pantycelyn~ value=~1~}~"}} {{Test if="hasItem(Sore Hands)" then="\n~- You injured your hands while escaping from [[Pantycelyn]]! **(-5pts)** ~{SetToken token=~finalscore~ value=~-5~}~ ~{SetToken token=~pantycelyn~ value=~1~}~"}} {{Test if="getToken(pantycelyn) = 0 and hasItem(RuthVarley)" then="\n~- You weren't involved in the [[Pantycelyn]] escape! **(0pts)**"}} {{Test if="getToken(pantycelyn) = 1 and hasItem(RuthVarley)" then="\n~- You single-handedly led the [[Pantycelyn]] escape! **(10pts)** ~{SetToken token=~finalscore~ value=~+10~}~"}} {{Test if="!hasItem(RuthVarley)" then="\n~- You didn't manage to rescue [[RuthVarley Ruth]] from [[Pantycelyn]]."}}

== [[Rocks]] And The RockMonkey == {{Test if="!hasItem(AndyKeohane) and !hasItem(Real Blue Rock) and !hasItem(Fake Blue Rock)" then="\n~- You didn't get a rock to satisfy AndyKeohane."}} {{Test if="hasItem(AndyKeohane) and hasItem(Real Blue Rock)" then="\n~- You got the **Real Blue Rock** from the GeographyTower. **(10pts) ~{SetToken token=~finalscore~ value=~+10~}~**"}} {{Test if="hasItem(AndyKeohane) and hasItem(Fake Blue Rock)" then="\n~- You made a convincing **Fake Blue Rock** by painting a normal rock. **(10pts) ~{SetToken token=~finalscore~ value=~+10~}~**"}}

== Cool Extras ==
~- {{Test if="hasItem(A Terrible Thing To Waste)" then="You finished with **A Terrible Thing To Waste** still in your possession. **(3pts)** ~{SetToken token=~finalscore~ value=~+3~}~" else="You never had (or managed to lose) **A Terrible Thing To Waste**. **(0pts)**"}}
~- {{Test if="hasItem(Welsh Recording)" then="You managed to make a **Welsh Recording**. **(2pts)** ~{SetToken token=~finalscore~ value=~+2~}~" else="You didn't manage to make a **Welsh Recording**. **(0pts)**"}} {{Test if="hasItem(PaulMann) and hasItem(JonAtkinson)" then="\n~- Getting PaulMann and JonAtkinson in the same room together without coming to blows. **(5pts)** ~{SetToken token=~finalscore~ value=~+5~}~"}}

== Death And Dying ==
~- {{Test if="getToken(tromanightdeath) = 0" then="You did not cheat by pressing the 'back' button after dying." else="You died, and pressed 'back' rather than starting over - cheater! **(-50pts)** ~{SetToken token=~finalscore~ value=~-50~}~"}}

