==== TromaNightAdventure ====
=== DanHuntley ===
----
**"How am I doing?"**

Dan assesses your progress: {{SetToken token="CanWin" value="1"}}

----
== TromaNight Stars ==
You need to get //three// TromaNight stars to join you, [[ClaireMelton Claire]], and I here at TheFlat. More stars means more points.

{{Test if="!hasItem(BrynSalisbury) and !hasItem(PaulMann) and !hasItem(RuthVarley) and !hasItem(MisterJTA) and !hasItem(JonAtkinson) and !hasItem(AndyKeohane)" then="\nYou haven't got **any** of the stars, yet!" else="The following stars have confirmed that they will be coming:\n~{InvListHas item=~BrynSalisbury/PaulMann/RuthVarley/MisterJTA/JonAtkinson/AndyKeohane~}~"}}

{{Test if="countItems(BrynSalisbury/PaulMann/RuthVarley/MisterJTA/JonAtkinson/AndyKeohane) < 3" then="**You still need to get more people to come!** ~{SetToken token=~CanWin~ value=~0~}~" else="**That's enough people for a successful TromaNight!**"}}
----
== TromaNight Films ==
You need to get //three// TromaNight films for us to watch. Extra films mean extra points.

{{Test if="!hasItem(Really Bad Film) and !hasItem(Really Good Film) and !hasItem(Moderately Good Film) and !hasItem(Arty Film) and !hasItem(Pornographic Film)" then="\nYou haven't found **any** films, yet!" else="We can watch any of the following films:\n~{InvListHas item=~Really Bad Film/Really Good Film/Moderately Good Film/Arty Film/Pornographic Film~}~"}}

{{Test if="countItems(Really Bad Film/Really Good Film/Moderately Good Film/Arty Film/Pornographic Film) < 3" then="**You still need to get more films!** ~{SetToken token=~CanWin~ value=~0~}~" else="**That's enough films for a successful TromaNight!**"}}
----
== TromaNight Refreshments ==
You need to get pizza to satisfy the people who are coming, and RealAle to drink.

{{Test if="!hasItem(RealAle) and !hasItem(Pizza With Meat) and !hasItem(Pizza With Vegetables) and !hasItem(Pizza With Everything)" then="\nYou haven't found **any** refreshments, yet!" else="We'll enjoy the following refreshments:\n~{InvListHas item=~RealAle/Pizza With Meat/Pizza With Vegetables/Pizza With Everything~}~"}}

{{Test if="!hasItem(RealAle) or countItems(Pizza With Meat/Pizza With Vegetables/Pizza With Everything) < 1" then="**You haven't satisfied the need for refreshments!** ~{SetToken token=~CanWin~ value=~0~}~" else="**That's enough to keep people satisfied!**"}}
----

//"That's your progess."// {{Test if="getToken(CanWin) = 1" then="\n\n----\n=== Ready To Win! ===\n\nYou've done enough things that you're ready to win! If you choose to win, no further score will be recorded, and you will be given a full score chart.\n----"}}

----
**What next?**
~- {{Test if="getToken(CanWin) = 1" then="**[[TromaNight230 WIN THE GAME!!!]]**" else="**WIN THE GAME!!!** (you haven't satisified the criteria to make this link available)"}}
~- [[TromaNightD01 "Back to it, then!"]]

==== TromaNightAdventure ====
=== ComputerScience Student ===
----
You show the Bar Of Soap to the [[CodeMonkey ComputerScience student]].

